  "texts": [
    "Controls included an NTC sgRNA and an overexpression (positive control) sgRNA targeting OCT4 (not a component of NeST:85).",
    "dCas9-VPR stable A549 cells were plated in a complete medium and transfected the next day with sgRNA plasmids for 24 h using FuGENE HD (Promega).",
    "Cells were selected with puromycin (0.44 µg ml -1) for 48 h and then lifted onto appropriate plates for further experimentation, where they were permitted to recover for 72 h. RNA was collected using the TRIzol reagent (Invitrogen, 15596026) and the RNeasy Mini kit (Qiagen, 74104).",
    "cDNA was synthesized using the iScript cDNA kit (Bio-Rad, 1708891).",
    "qPCR was performed using SYBR green, and cycle threshold (C t) values were compared for genes overexpressed by CRISPRa versus NTC samples (Extended Data Fig. 4c and Supplementary Table 4)."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}